+All validation commands pass. Here's what was implemented:
+
+**Modules:**
+- **Plugin Registry** (`src/registry/index.ts`): SQLite-backed catalog with add, get, list, search, remove, listVersions, and update operations
+- **Version Resolver** (`src/resolver/index.ts`): Semver-based version resolution with satisfies, maxSatisfying, validRange, and resolve methods
+- **Sandboxed Runner** (`src/runner/index.ts`): VM-based code execution with timeout support and memory/duration tracking
+- **Review System** (`src/reviews/index.ts`): SQLite-backed reviews with ratings, comments, flagging, and average calculations
+- **Dependency Graph** (`src/deps/index.ts`): Tree building, cycle detection, topological sort, and dependency flattening
+
+**Integration** (`src/index.ts`): `createMarketplace()` function composing all services with `installPlugin()` workflow that validates manifests, registers plugins, resolves dependencies, detects cycles, and executes entry points in the sandbox.
+
+**Tests**: 42 tests covering all modules and the integration layer.
